\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223797904284/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3c36bcf4-1dc4-4c31-a354-96df752c4b40\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a7c86ea8-2522-4d1b-ab13-0f72320d4076\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4cf66af6-2980-4e36-8d80-c7722b90fe43\" style=\"color:#555555;\">위 이미지는 접었을 때 A4 사이즈가 되는 리플렛입니다. 이건 보통 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-beec17e6-f37f-4c15-a5cb-a2ac9c581d2f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>210mm × 4 = 840mm</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-62a877e7-52b5-4e4d-9066-a1e239692870\" style=\"color:#555555;\">로 작업됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-51a55672-3052-4f54-a6f3-e777b609cc83\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a344bbe2-eadc-4c0e-96c4-dcccff9d7c9b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7acf17ac-934c-4619-a7b2-75cf94c1099d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2e6a0ae6-29cd-4842-a3a5-eac659b89f07\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">그런 이유로 접었을 때 A4와 A4를 어떻게 접는 냐는 사이즈와 단가에서 차이가 많이 나므로 소통하실 때 주의하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-4101916d-9615-4780-8684-4e967e96a31e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-sectio