nt-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:664px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223797904284/011.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-91e612bd-9427-4c11-ad36-8b0884c6b40f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7316d629-49be-49b2-8836-222459ac4da8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-872d1fe6-e43e-43dc-a1cc-e7b75b3c5e46\" style=\"color:#555555;\">병풍 접지는 병풍 모양처럼 접기 때문에 디자인 배열이나 순서를 생각하지 않으셔도 됩니다. 정접지는 중간에 맨 뒤 페이지가 존재하는 형식이라 레이아웃이나 기타 고려해야 할 부분이 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c3393a8f-1c1a-4d53-821a-ec096f1bf9c0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7a74ba2b-8713-456d-834a-a70da1b2865c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디자인 시 페이지 배열에 신경쓰세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-447e1e27-2cbf-4bd4-9c6c-06aadda25e96\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-273a436c-06b9-4ae3-a9e3-fae8375110d7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8d97f911-a2a7-4a30-9684-835edf5ca8cf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7325043e-f007-4587-868f-5b23f2943e2e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">또한 대문 접지 등은 가운데 접히는 부분의 여백을 1mm 짧게 제작해야 되는 등 고려해야 할 사항들이 있지만 병풍 접지는 가장 간단하게 제약사항 없이 접을 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e0ce0e21-7ae8-459d-802c-d51d5a05cb6f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-388aa8f9-8540-4a76-92ed-e68f804d7e96\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-8fa01a41-6787-4560-8987-55113d8b0aef\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a5247c25-71ea-4523-a05a-4bd9a1448eb6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-441b6634-e7f9-4f5b-81b9-78eabe2524a5\" style=\"\">4단 대문 접지</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-77f4dded-f5fa-4404-b220-1682ac0a4ba2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5373fd29-5c57-4a41-86c4-2a44c458a8b0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f87ede77-ab32-40f1-a1f4-7bf0b6ff9c8e\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>4단 리플릿 중에</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f2d3f339-2569-4827-a58b-ce3530f9b21a\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 대문 접지는 대문 모양으로 열어서 펼칠 수 있는 모양입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d27