ss=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223797904284/017.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3e5dce79-2cee-4baf-a202-b8fa01e326f9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-20cc56b4-e583-4e22-822f-ff03cb0eef95\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8fed52ac-ce27-4317-9fd3-79242ec33e27\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>문의하시면 각 사이즈마다 작업 템플릿을 보내드리겠습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-77db9105-4fd5-4d19-bd58-f79d124687b7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-592b26c1-06dd-4649-96a5-52efb3b58357\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6cd0d629-221f-4649-8cd9-ee788ea80c31\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e0a9077c-8cc5-4a13-9e23-a7104780d7fe\" style=\"color:#555555;\">대문 접지에서 밖으로 감싸지는 부분의 접지 방법이 다릅니다. 그러므로 디자인 파일의 페이지 위치를 잘 접어 보시고 결정하시면 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b1d3a99c-6ebe-4b28-8142-9ccbdab8ecad\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:633px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223797904284/018.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fba647fb-a8f8-4c12-89ed-9427e9b4bc26\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f778f998-50d4-4c29-8e02-d4b8bb9eebdb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fb73f1ea-7121-4d66-b9cc-8817473a1376\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이런 디자인으로 접히게 되므로 접히는 부분의 안쪽을 어느 부분에서 1mm 정도 작게 결정해야 되는지를 잘 판단하시고 디자인해 주십시오.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-ef597bc5-5b0a-4108-8220-17058c13f0b2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8e480cc5-dec4-4d16-be59-c75ea6a3b3ae\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-ecfc5a30-837e-4aa5-80d5-cb12f1e34747\" style=\"\">4단 접지 사이즈</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3f333b06-0ec4-4cb1-a925-5e30d3f7bf12\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223797904284/019.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9bef108d-fd65-4d91-926a-002bdf7c9340\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-430cc3f8-ccb4-4b4b-ac33-c1215d5e20b1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-39776c59-f968-4d63-9107-7ddf0b68ce10\" style=\"color:#555555;\">사이즈는 자유롭게 진행할 수 있지만 종이의 절수에 맞는 가장 효율적인 디자인 제일 좋습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-427ac5d8-02c1-41ae-94ae-afbe55da924a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-070205f2-5673-40dd-91f2-8da3c04cd04b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7bf30f22-8725-44b1-9621-58133dcbbe8c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-be6d2cac-123e-4e47-bf99-56235e52a6f1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">고객님도 알 수 있듯이 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d827683b-1a15-44a2-b305-e7bb22598682\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>국전 사이즈는 939mm × 636mm</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9c5f4efe-880f-4411-9152-3fd1938ce2c2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다. 이런 이유로 4단 리플렛의 가장 좋은 사이즈 즉 종이를 계산한 가장 효율적인 사이즈는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-52fa76c3-3de0-4346-ad5b-6ad7019bb985\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3ab3ce48-95cf-4576-8bae-bac16aadb74f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-949303e8-b5a9-4716-84d1-1a80fa2ce0d9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-20982109-f723-428c-b161-dffa40c07169\" style=\"color:#555555;\">600mm × 297mm입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9d9f2f49-de62-4645-b2fd-09cd4d1937d8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6bc27342-c37b-49cf-8066-9a905bd14bb7\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>접었을 때 150mm × 297mm</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fd9a53c2-35df-43e7-b9b8-01fc3c4e88ae\" style=\"color:#555555;\">으로 가장 많이 작업을 하십니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ea0acfcf-6a62-496e-983f-f01437c2a430\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-335dcb07-c774-4695-ad33-b2c1c7b36dd1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a1cd7343-7046-4f73-848f-a71aba9f0dbe\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3a3355b2-01cf-492f-8953-ca53ea4e30d6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 사이즈면 국전지에 3판이 조판(하리꼬미)되어 1R을 인쇄하게 되면 1,500장 인쇄되어 나옵니다. 100% 효율적이라고 할 수는 없지만 종이의 로스를 고려할 때 이 사이즈가 가장 일반적인 사이즈입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-84df0fb9-402d-4b86-9738-54867086cc89\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7ef5a43d-dcc0-47bc-b49b-05298933fbf2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7fb2042f-ef5c-48b1-beb9-0f585c69daa5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223797904284/020.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-96d87751-ceef-4015-b022-442baba67147\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3dae0c49-c961-462a-958e-056e304d826d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2238934f-4d3f-4f37-9f07-cf298fb5347a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">편집 사이즈는 회사마다 다르지만 2~3mm 정도를 사방으로 빼주시면 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fbb145dd-8b3a-4e32-a177-e59aa2a620bf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b2fb6e0d-fb56-4954-b1fc-828727e262af\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b5e5c81f-627e-4690-a626-1a597141dbee\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-445eeb58-a74b-45a7-b4b8-3512b5d42ac6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">여기서 주의할 점은 접지 형태마다 접었을 때 1mm 정도를 짧게 디자인하여 잘 접힐 수 있도록 작업하는 것입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-dded6e9e-d9a8-4dc8-9a7c-c2be4e57f4d4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-76812257-d1a0-40de-a52a-69d7b232d212\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e247d4f0-a5dd-4737-8ff8-74624cbdfea9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca4773c-0af0-4f14-bffa-8ea60d9af8dd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">예를 들어 대문 접지의 예시입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-70b4eda8-dfc6-4e09-86ef-70eaabf9c7a3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223797904284/021.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1e6712ed-5b19-46f1-8adc-99991deab13b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b7f05865-1cb5-4973-8838-50d26d9fa3b2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-189066b6-5b1b-494e-84db-c9d8aa22e3b4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">위의 이미지처럼 가장자리에 접히는 부분의 단면적을 약 1mm 정도를 줄여서 접었을 때 딱 붙어서 접지가 구겨지거나 삐뚤어지지 않게 하는 것이 좋습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-14dabf38-c50b-4e3c-adb2-fe3d7179e042\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3c96abe0-f255-466b-8260-5e8915c36542\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bde84205-80bd-48ce-ae69-462f82956e8c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-633b64b5-e975-41c4-9082-ee978029abe3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">물론 이 여분은 종이의 두께나 기타 등등을 고려하여 작업해야 합니다. 두꺼운 종이는 조금 더 여분을 둘 수 있습니다. 하지만 거의 1mm 면 크게 문제가 없는 것이 저희의 경험입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bfa4304c-abae-4f44-b067-1cfb29049717\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-311209c9-3d0c-481d-8502-1dbd413b05c9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-25bd0aae-bb9f-4862-ae60-17c0ae6e0701\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1710edd6-6591-4ca8-9d02-46f84f3b2080\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이런 이유로 단이 많은 리플렛은 절대 두꺼운 정이를 선택하지 않으십니다. 만약 예를 들어 300g으로 4단, 5단 심지어 6단 접지를 만든다면 접었을 때 모양이 바르게 나오지 않을 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ebbb8446-4678-405f-8d56-9eb0967d4be5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1372f5ae-26bd-4177-be9b-cf89cb5c283f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-75b025dc-860f-4acd-bf4a-90f9c8074333\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-172f49fc-99fb-4f24-b848-a0d0142c8914\" style=\"color:#555555;\">4단 리플렛에서 가장 많이 사용되는 종이 평량은 100g ~ 180g 사이입니다. 이 사이 평량을 가진 종이들이 많이 사용됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-75493f9f-99cd-4c61-ae03-b8a38c865d5f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7a509329-f80b-4764-ada6-400acfe028f6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5e7e4acf-b3a1-4e0e-8313-9ce36156e380\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-672db24d-259d-494f-ad14-c3f42730f5e8\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>랑데뷰 130g ~ 160g 종이 계열이 단이 많은 리플렛에서 가장 많이 사용됩니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-476a9319-be2d-4a5f-a458-f47e51f38e4d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-12645614-9072-4f35-9fca-5d17cc0f5dee\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ccc048f6-1051-4712-a4bc-8893a5dfd84f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f9af37cf-f385-40cd-83f1-770bb0f9d71c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그리고 평량에 따라 오시를 넣고 접어야 안전하게 진행될 수 있습니다. 오시를 넣어야 하는 평량은 150g 이상이 일반적입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-04feef5c-2fe4-4fbb-b8ee-d19deb300e83\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8e1babf9-97d9-4cd8-89e0-0573ffad52f2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-e1b4c87d-4ca9-4b0d-96a1-ed621d7e7a2e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d2bda53a-2f5b-4052-a3a5-4b9397d90ba7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-cda85f25-6afb-4805-9b7a-0b7398a2ccaf\" style=\"\">결론</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1285a1ca-f6e2-4c78-9f4a-b917b6707824\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-54a77b65-a297-4aa7-a643-3d2138bd03d0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-35788128-db0c-4d96-86b4-f9bd0187880f\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>4단 접지물의 사이즈</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-91e52f12-f66c-4a90-90c7-5e469e9a3c67\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b> : 600mm × 297mm</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a1837b28-6da5-4a57-ae19-0d0dbfd8a5c7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-4d97e64a-7673-4232-8da5-6f63cdbf80be\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>인쇄 </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-477c26b6-6fd1-431b-a809-9ba9d36fac78\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>: 양면 칼라 : 종이에 따라 UV 인쇄를 해야 할 수 있습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7e7b736e-288a-4c69-97bf-95c6e2ea3f95\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0e3ed5c1-361f-45a3-8d73-b58fd12a5e66\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>접지</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-c45a520a-405c-4654-9464-50833730f5cd\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b> : 4단 접지</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c948e364-c205-4655-b899-c2eaf265b118\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-79477f39-7056-4dcb-983b-c6298119074b\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>종이</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-fa74fa39-886e-4347-bfa2-a1ba3d141011\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b> : 110g ~ 180g 사이 평량</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-dbbb70e7-61e2-4b3d-9cf5-5dd618089a67\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1a4d287c-4920-4006-8496-b705a4a3b8ec\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4b3ba973-f43e-4434-8063-e0939eeafaab\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1f4d810d-0327-404d-96c1-79e370b8fe15\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 고객과의 꼼꼼한 소통을 통해 가장 빠르고 정확하게 인쇄물을 제작하고 있습니다. 언제든 문의하시면 소통하고 가장 완벽한 디자인으로 제작해 드리겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1418b90c-befd-4fc1-8b9e-69500b0bf9bc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F223797904284#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}